name: Filterplugin
tagline: A jQuery plugin to filter arrays based in user input.
body:
### FilterPlugin
This Plugin simply hooks up an input field to filter through an array of results, and display those results on the page.

```
$('#myInputField).filterPluing(arrayToFilter [,options]);
```


arrayToFiler must be an array of string literals.
options must be an object, containing zero or more properties from the following:
```
{
    caseSenstive: true, // Default is true
    wholeWords: false // Default is false
}
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
